%N A395711 Expansion of g^7*(7*g-6)/(6-5*g)^4, where g = 1+x*g^6 is the g.f. of A002295.
%F A395711 a(n) = (n+1) * A386567(n+1).
%F A395711 G.f.: (Sum_{k>=0} (6*k+2)/(3*k+2) * binomial(6*k+4,k) * x^k) * (Sum_{k>=0} binomial(6*k,k) * x^k)^3.
%F A395711 Sum_{k>=1} a(k-1) * x^k/k^2 = (1/5) * log( Sum_{k>=0} binomial(6*k-1,k) * x^k ).
%F A395711 a(n) = (n+1) * Sum_{k=0..n} binomial(6*k+5+l,k) * binomial(6*n-6*k-l,n-k) for every real number l.
%F A395711 a(n) = (n+1) * Sum_{k=0..n} 5^(n-k) * binomial(6*n+6,k).
%F A395711 a(n) = (n+1) * Sum_{k=0..n} 6^(n-k) * binomial(5*n+k+5,k).
%o A395711 (PARI) a(n) = (n+1)*sum(k=0, n, 5^(n-k)*binomial(6*n+6, k));
